Hey!!Today I woke up and went to art camp.Today wuz r last class so we got to bring back ur favorite things.I brought back everything!lOl!!Then we made pictures coppied them on to styriphome and put ink on em nd then mounted them on to blu wrapping paper on a black constrouction paper on the back.I made a mommy manatee with her baby hugging her.Then we made pictures and coppied them onto scrathboards.I picked a blu scratchboard and a bird on a stick with a moon a butterfly and another tree in the background.I did a cool texture like holes like wood has.The rest parts were collererd in.Then we made pens but this time we used micro beads nd it worked sssooooo much better I made 3 cuz I left mine there and i pulled the other beads off nd made another.Then we made flower pics. out of paint nd me nd carly were mixing colors!Then we made 1 more pen but I made two cuz da 1 from yesterday.I had a total of 3 pens.Then me Rachel nd Carly were playin in da lake while Carlys mom talked to mrs.bryant nd Camren her niece who spent the night at her house for the week for the art played with us nd they kept putting grass in my hair.Then we threw the hedgehog at Rachel and Mrs.Bryant said thats enough so we stoped but Rachel threw it after mrs.bryant said not 2 nd got in deep troubble!So then we went home a little later and I made a lunch bucket nd had a 4th of july cake. Then I talked to Letycia nd Christina on the phone.Then I went to gymnastics nd did well.We practiced front handsprings today nd the rest wuz da same backhadspring nd ariel still got but keep falling on my but!Then me nd my mom went to the mall nd I bought a lipgloss (watermellon) at the dollar store we only walked to Charolette Russe nd we parked  at dillards.Then my total was 1.07 and I gave her a dollar bill nd 1 quarter I got change back but I forget how much.Then me my mom nd dad went to Papa Tonys nd I got a lemonade w/ somthing on the kids menu I forget wut its called but it wuz a giant meatball sitting in noodles.Then we got a lrg. pizza for the table nd my dad got a water my mom got a iced tea nd they both got some chicken thing or it looked liked but my mom got a soup w/ hers I forget wut kind so it wuz a little diffrent from my dads.Then we all had bread.Then when I went to the bathroom my dad wuz waiting outside nd watched the waitress burn her arm on the boiling water.But when I wuz in the bathroom u opened the door nd there wuz the sink then u open another door to da potty.Well then we left nd im watching the Ronald Reagon burial witch has been on for a lot of days but so entertaining yet so said!Aww.Im upset he died nd I almost cried.For real!Im online now nd will soon be going to bed.
